title: Dr. Gene Scott Unband with Ron Spann
description:
Files like this were pulled from the internet by Gene Scotts widow shorty after his death.
These were recorded by me in the 1980's on 6 hour home VHS video tape from my C Band satellite dish. Sorry about the poor quality.
